data.description: HOME BACKS UP TO CAPE FEAR RIVER, RO SYSTEM IN BATHROOM AND KITCHEN SINKS. Brand new HVAC system & ducts MAY 2023.Well laid out ranch on an acre on the river! Fish from your own backyard! This home is the highest house on the river. Not only is it dry but there is wildlife everywhere. You can watch deer across the river, ducks, squirrels and rabbits. The large screened in porch over looking the tree covered yard and river views is the perfect place to spend the morning. This 3 bed 2 bath ranch is perfect for someone wanting some space and enjoys the outdoors. Spacious kitchen with a great lay out to include new ceramic tile that overlooks the family room. Bedrooms are generous and the home is smartly laid out with no wasted space. Not only do you get maximum living for your dollar but you still do it in a home that will not be expensive to maintain. Large wired shed/storage building on site as well to hold all your toys or turn it into a workshop. Less than 30 minutes to Ft Bragg!!!
